Package edu.rpi.legup.ui.proofeditorui.treeview

package edu.rpi.legup.ui.proofeditorui.treeview
  • Class
    Description
    TreeElementView
    Abstract base class for views of tree elements in the tree structure.
    TreeNodeView
    Represents a view of a tree node in the tree structure.
    TreePanel
    TreePanel is a JPanel that manages and displays a tree view with associated toolbar and status information.
    TreeToolBarButton
    TreeToolBarButton is a JButton that represents a button in the tree toolbar.
    TreeToolBarName
    TreeToolBarName defines the names of actions represented by buttons in the tree toolbar.
    TreeToolbarPanel
    TreeToolbarPanel is a JPanel that provides a toolbar for managing tree elements in the tree view.
    TreeTransitionView
    TreeTransitionView is a visual representation of a tree transition in the tree view.
    TreeView
    The TreeView class provides a graphical representation of a Tree structure, allowing interaction and visualization of tree elements, transitions, and selections.
    TreeViewSelection
    TreeViewSelection manages the selection and hover state of tree element views in a tree view.
